title: NMU Alumnus Named Outdoor Educator of the Year (Northern Michigan University)
text: ( Source : Northern Michigan University ) Outgoing President Anne Jeannette LaSovage presents the award to Stobie NMU alumnus Pete Stobie was named Outdoor Educator of the Year by the Michigan Alliance for Environmental and Outdoor Education .
